<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Responsive Services Section</title>
    <!-- Font Awesome CDN-->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0-beta3/css/all.min.css" />
    <script src="https://kit.fontawesome.com/3a918a3b74.js" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
    <!-- Google Font -->
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@400;500;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />
    <!-- Stylesheet -->
    <style>
        * {
    padding: 0;
    margin: 0;
    box-sizing: border-box;
    font-family: Nunito, sans-serif;
  }
  section {
    width: 100%;
    display: grid;
    place-items: center;
  }
  .row {
    margin-top: 20px;
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }
  .column {
    width: 100%;
    padding: 0 1em 1em 1em;
    text-align: center;
  }
  .card {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    padding: 2em 1.5em;
    background: linear-gradient(#ffffff 50%, #2c7bfe 50%);
    background-size: 100% 200%;
    background-position: 0 2.5%;
    border-radius: 5px;
    box-shadow: 0 0 35px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.12);
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: 0.5s;
  }
  h3 {
    font-size: 20px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: #1f194c;
    margin: 1em 0;
  }
  p {
    color: #575a7b;
    font-size: 15px;
    line-height: 1.6;
    letter-spacing: 0.03em;
  }
  .icon-wrapper {
    background-color: #2c7bfe;
    position: relative;
    margin: auto;
    font-size: 30px;
    height: 2.5em;
    width: 2.5em;
    color: #ffffff;
    border-radius: 50%;
    display: grid;
    place-items: center;
    transition: 0.5s;
  }
  .card:hover {
    background-position: 0 100%;
  }
  .card:hover .icon-wrapper {
    background-color: #ffffff;
    color: #2c7bfe;
  }
  .card:hover h3 {
    color: #ffffff;
  }
  .card:hover p {
    color: #f0f0f0;
  }
  @media screen and (min-width: 768px) {
    section {
      padding: 0 2em;
    }
    .column {
      flex: 0 50%;
      max-width: 50%;
    }
  }
  @media screen and (min-width: 992px) {
    section {
      padding: 1em 3em;
    }
    .column {
      flex: 0 0 33.33%;
      max-width: 33.33%;
    }
  }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <section>
        <div class="row">
            <h2 class="section-heading" style="font-size: 36px;">Why US?</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="row">
            <div class="column">
                <div class="card">
                    <div class="icon-wrapper">
                        <i class="fas fa-person-chalkboard"></i>
                    </div>
                    <h3>Expert Guidance</h3>
                    <p>
                        At Eshida, we boast a team of highly qualified professionals with advanced degrees and
                        real-world experience in their respective fields. This means students receive support that is
                        not only academically sound but also practically relevant, providing them with a deeper
                        understanding of their subjects.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="column">
                <div class="card">
                    <div class="icon-wrapper">
                        <i class="fa-solid fa-headset"></i>
                    </div>
                    <h3>Customized Support</h3>
                    <p>
                        We understand that every student has unique needs and learning styles. Eshida offers
                        personalized support tailored to each student's specific requirements, ensuring that our
                        assistance is as effective as possible in helping them achieve their academic goals.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="column">
                <div class="card">
                    <div class="icon-wrapper">
                        <i class="fas fa-shield-alt"></i>
                    </div>
                    <h3>Commitment to Integrity</h3>
                    <p>
                        Eshida is founded on principles of academic honesty and integrity. We provide students with
                        tools and support to enhance their learning while ensuring that they uphold the highest
                        standards of academic conduct. Our services are designed to complement their education, not
                        compromise it.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="column">
                <div class="card">
                    <div class="icon-wrapper">
                        <i class="fa-solid fa-clock"></i>
                    </div>
                    <h3>Timely Assistance</h3>
                    <p>
                        We know that deadlines are critical in the academic world. Eshida is committed to delivering
                        timely support to help students manage their time effectively and meet their deadlines without
                        compromising on the quality of their work.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="column">
                <div class="card">
                    <div class="icon-wrapper">
                        <i class="fa-solid fa-dna"></i>
                    </div>
                    <h3>Innovative Solutions</h3>
                    <p>
                        With a focus on leveraging the latest educational technologies and methodologies, Eshida offers
                        innovative solutions to academic challenges. Whether it's through cutting-edge research tools or
                        creative approaches to learning and project execution, we ensure students have access to the
                        best resources.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="column">
                <div class="card">
                    <div class="icon-wrapper">
                        <i class="fas fa-rocket"></i>
                    </div>
                    <h3>Empowering Students for the Future</h3>
                    <p>
                        Beyond immediate academic projects, Eshida's goal is to equip students with skills that will
                        serve them well beyond their academic careers. From critical thinking and research to effective
                        communication and time management, we prepare students for success in their future endeavors.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
</body>

</html>